{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2fead91817","title":"江青关于拍摄《太阳与地球》影片给王洪文李先念吴德的信","origin":"文化部办公厅提供","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"34bde3e5d7","index":0,"year":1974,"month":6,"day":14,"articleId":"2fead91817"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"33f01f9c5a","name":"李先念","type":"人物"},{"id":"7f0393737e","name":"吴德","type":"人物"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"8e2c446eb1","name":"王洪文","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"16d8bb085a","type":"title","text":"江青关于拍摄《太阳与地球》影片给王洪文李先念吴德的信","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2fead91817"},{"id":"0c7e8834bc","type":"authors","text":"江青","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2fead91817"},{"id":"6c3ef1a3da","type":"subtitle","text":"江青在科影厂关于拍摄《太阳与地球》影片的信件上的批语","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2fead91817"},{"id":"8560949725","type":"appellation","text":"洪文、先念、吴德同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2fead91817"},{"id":"2ed50ba26c","type":"paragraph","text":"这是件大事，不仅青少年需要。我们这样的人也需要学习这种知识。北京天文馆被外国人占领了，只有中国人一个画面。而天文学是中国最早发现的，并且有大量的历史记载，单是二十四史上就占有很大篇幅。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2fead91817"},{"id":"322bdcf4ad","type":"paragraph","text":"有些中国人不象中国人，外国人放个屁都是香的，应该批判他们。我们建议支持拍电影，并组织一个班子专门整理、研究祖国的天文学。以上意见妥否？请批示。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2fead91817"},{"id":"8db4028fb1","type":"paragraph","text":" 江青一九七四年六月十四日  拂晓","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2fead91817"},{"id":"87c822a5b4","type":"appellation","text":"（文化部办公厅提供）","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2fead91817"}],"page":{"id":"6cb63f6473","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2fead91817","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}